# Binary files
# ============
*.db     binary
*.p      binary
*.pkl    binary
*.pickle binary
*.pyc    binary
*.pyd    binary
*.pyo    binary

# Jupyter notebook
*.ipynb  text

# Note: .db, .p, and .pkl files are associated
# with the python modules ``pickle``, ``dbm.*``,
# ``shelve``, ``marshal``, ``anydbm``, & ``bsddb``
